A DoomLike 2.5D Engine (DLE) by Alpyre

Build with SAS/C v6.58 (with the provided makefile)

Controls:
wasd : Movement and look around
F1   : Toggle FPS counter
F2   : Toggle sectorID display
f    : Toggle full screen
ESC  : Quit

---------------------
Development History |
---------------------

0.4.8b (17.09.2017): - load textures to fastMem where available
                     - removal of some visual bugs
                     - change keybindings
                     - optimize (by removing some unnecessary calculations)

0.4.2b (26.07.2017): - a complete redesign of the wall loop and portal evaluation.
                       now only transforms the first vertex and calculates
                       the rest by adding a unit vector (nightlord's advice).

0.3.1b (09.07.2017): - Replaced perspective correct texture mapping algorithm
                       with an affine mapping one.

0.2.1b (22.06.2017): - all floating point operations are replaced with
                       integer ones.

0.1.1b (16.06.2017): - now only draws the upper part of the horizon
                       and reverse blit copies it to the bottom.

0.0.2b (15.06.2017): - optimizations.

0.0.1b (18.05.2017): - first working development version.
